com.google.android.glass.TMM

Class HeadScrollView

  • java.lang.Object
    • ScrollView
      • com.google.android.glass.TMM.HeadScrollView

  • public class HeadScrollView
extends ScrollView
    The Class HeadScrollView. This view provides a scrollview that is linked to a sensor listener. This allows the user to scroll up and down the view using head motions, which simulates (roughly) reading down a wall of text.

        public static final int HEAD_MOVEMENT_DEG
        The Constant HEAD_MOVEMENT_DEG. This is set to the maximum degrees that a person must move their head to read the entire contents of a card, regardless of its length.
